      "description": "Offering an investment-grade 1994 Toyota Supra Turbo in concours condition. This specimen features the iconic 2JZ-GTE twin-scroll, sequential turbocharged inline-six, delivering a flat torque curve and impeccable throttle response. The powertrain is paired with the original Getrag V160 six-speed manual gearbox, providing precise gate engagement and zero drivetrain lash. The chassis retains absolute structural rigidity with all factory-original VIN tags and spot welds intact. Mechanically unmolested, it features the factory-spec Torsen limited-slip differential and active aero components. The undercarriage is free of oxidation, and the engine maintains optimal compression across all cylinders, reflecting a lifetime of climate-controlled storage and rigorous preventative maintenance.",
