      "description": "Presenting a truly collector-grade specimen that redefines the standard for 'mint' condition. This vehicle has been exclusively garage-kept in a climate-controlled environment and it shows. The exterior retains its original factory luster, protected by a professional-grade ceramic coating; there are zero stone chips, swirl marks, or curb rash on the pristine alloy wheels. Inside, the cabin remains in showroom state\u2014the premium leather bolsters show no signs of compression, the 'new car' scent persists, and it has never been smoked in. Mechanically, this car is beyond reproach. I have maintained a meticulous binder of every service record from day one, including a recent comprehensive fluid flush and multi-point inspection that returned a flawless report. Every electronic feature, from the panoramic sunroof to the advanced driver assistance systems, functions exactly as it did the day it rolled off the assembly line. This is not just a used car; it is a time capsule for the discerning buyer who refuses to settle for anything less than perfection. Includes all original keys, owner\u2019s manuals, and a custom car cover.",
